{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-sheet-js","path":"/sheets/pandoc","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Pandoc 是一个文本格式转换工具。</p>\n<!-- more -->\n<h2 id=\"链接\">链接</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://pandoc.org/\">官网</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pandoc.org/getting-started.html\">基础指南</a>，面对不会命令行的人士<br>\n<a href=\"https://pandoc.org/MANUAL.html\">用户手册</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"支持的格式\">支持的格式</h2>\n<p>以下列出部分常用的格式。完整列表见官网。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Markdown</li>\n<li>LaTeX</li>\n<li>Microsoft Word(.docx)</li>\n<li>HTML</li>\n<li>EPUB</li>\n<li>OPML</li>\n<li>Jupyter Notebook</li>\n<li>reStructuredText</li>\n</ul>\n<p>以上格式支持导入和导出。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>reveal.js</li>\n<li>Microsoft Powerpoint(.pptx)</li>\n<li>LaTeX Beamer</li>\n<li>PDF</li>\n</ul>\n<p>以上格式仅支持导出。</p>\n<h2 id=\"基本用法\">基本用法</h2>\n<p>Pandoc 可以根据扩展名自动检测导入导出类型。</p>\n<p>使用 <code>-o</code> 或 <code>--output=\"foo\"</code> 导出文件。如果文件设为 <code>-</code> 则直接打印到控制台。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ pandoc <span class=\"token string\">'[导入]'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    -o <span class=\"token string\">'[导出]'</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>使用 <code>-f</code> 指定导入格式，<code>-t</code> 指定导出格式。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ pandoc <span class=\"token string\">'[导入]'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    -f <span class=\"token string\">'[导入格式]'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    -t <span class=\"token string\">'[导出格式]'</span></code></pre></div>\n<!--\n```shell\npandoc test.md --bibliography my.bib --csl china-national-standard-gb-t-7714-2015-author-date.csl -o test.docx\n```\n-->\n<h2 id=\"参考文献\">参考文献</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ pandoc <span class=\"token string\">'[导入]'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    -C <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --bibliography <span class=\"token string\">'[文献数据]'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --csl <span class=\"token string\">'[CSL]'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    -o <span class=\"token string\">'[导出]'</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Pandoc 速查表","date":"2020/12/30","category":"信息学","tags":["工具"],"keywords":["文本处理"]},"fields":{"modifiedTime":"2021/04/26"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"sheets/pandoc","quarter":"sheets"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2243046057","63159454"]}